node.text: “I love to touch different kinds of art[s] and crafts. I like to sew, I like to knit, I like to paint, to do ceramics," says French artist @nathalie_lete of her ever-inspired creative process. "In my work I try to put all of my feelings inside. I, myself, am like a big kid in my soul.” Here, she welcomes us inside her eclectic Paris studio, where whimsical vignettes and vintage treasures delight and inspire 🎨🌷🍄
